# Figures will be placed here.
#
# Naming convention: `NN_short-slug.{png,pdf,svg}` where `NN` matches the
# leading two-digit section number that consumes the figure, and the slug
# is a short kebab-case description. PDF preferred for vector, PNG for
# bitmap, SVG kept alongside for source.
#
# Example: `02_hardpoint-layout.pdf` for the platform hardpoint diagram.
